leads.lead_text: Leaves ovate to suborbicular, more or less flat; male flowers with sepals ovate, c. 1 mm long, often reddish; stamens all less than 1 mm long
Leaves oblong-elliptic, concave above; male flowers with sepals more or less oblong, c. 2 mm long, whitish; 3 inner stamens 1 mm long or more
